{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_01","textHome":"很不错吧？这部旅行房车。可是由我一步步改@造而成的。凭借这个，就能在全国各地巡游@，拯救那些因无法战斗而痛苦的魔法少女了@。机会难得，你要不要也来我这进行调整？@我莉薇娅·梅黛洛斯会亲自来摆弄你的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_17","textHome":"城市里的地盘争夺很激烈啊。虽说我们是中立@的，但实在是太容易引人注目了一直都很烦@啊。只取得信任也要花费很多卡路里啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_18","textHome":"虽然也有纯粹的实现了希望的少女，但也有将@绝望当成希望实现了的孩子。我就像是负责@接受那些孩子的容器吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_19","textHome":"那么，Puella Care的表演也该开@始了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_20","textHome":"虽说这是自己想出来的技术，但真有趣啊。感@觉身体变轻了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_21","textHome":"我要是不在了的话，就不能再拯救其他痛苦中@的孩子了吧。如果我死了的话，就不能将夜@鹤和月出里养育成人了，所以我还不会死的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_22","textHome":"一切都是为了万物，为了掌控它的宇宙，即使@不愿意我也只能那样做。但只要我还在宏大@的目的下行动，就会让我重要的孩子们陷入@不幸。所以我再次发誓，我将成为拥有伟大@意志的我"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_23","textHome":"本来连战斗都不被允许的我，是没有权利去杀@害期盼着希望的魔法少女们。不如说是将进@行调整一事当作是慢慢赎罪。也就是说我打@算一直为大家进行调整，直到我死去为止"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_24","textHome":"谢谢你每次都来关照我。点数也积累了不少了@吧？就让我来服务你吧，如果有什么要求的@话我会听的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_25","textHome":"早上好哦。一大早就被吓了一跳吧？毕竟是被@一群动来动去的扑克牌给叫醒的啊。哼哼，@这就是我的魔法哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_26","textHome":"哈？来玩的话好歹考虑一下时间啊。夜鹤跟月@出里都还在学校。虽说这样，难得来一次…@对了，要在这吃午饭吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_02","textHome":"我是莉薇娅·梅黛洛斯。现在流动到了神滨，@经营着一间3人的巡回调整屋，要是有兴趣@的话随时都能来。会热情服务你的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_27","textHome":"太阳会转来转去在各个国家之间巡回吧…？所@以，将希望被送到祖国的父母能健康生活的@心意传递给夕阳，夕阳一定会送达的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_28","textHome":"好了，再往里面靠一点啊。我家的床本来就很@小了，4个人一起进去的话就塞满了。不凑@紧一点，做到紧挨着身子的话是不行的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_29","textHome":"不是不是不是，我可不是关西人哦？这种说话@方式，只是因为能很好地进行沟通才维持着@这样哦"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_30","textHome":"不行不行，现在你不用害怕了，放轻松吧。不@能很好的进行调整的话不仅是浪费了金钱，@而且还无法打倒魔女吧？好了，再挑战一次@吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_31","textHome":"所谓无尽境界…真是，还有那么奇妙的魔女在@啊…。不过，总觉得在哪里有感知到过同样@的魔力反应…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_32","textHome":"这可不得了！魔法少女聚在一起大战啊！不行@不行，这是金钱的香气啊！夜鹤、月出里，@该巡回调整屋登场了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_33","textHome":"真的，有夜鹤和月出里跟着真是帮忙了。像这@样有无数的势力的话一个人是看不过来的啊@。今天也是一如既往的忙啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_34","textHome":"刚好也有空，教你一个魔术吧？只需一枚硬币@便能让人大吃一惊。作为话题可是最好不过@了吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_35","textHome":"浴…浴缸…想泡在浴缸里啊—！不行！旅行房@车里只能淋浴是不行的啊！我可以借你们家@的浴室吗！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_36","textHome":"咕呜!!…………开玩笑的，哈哈，你刚是觉@得我真的死了吧？这就是我的自伤魔术。血@液也很真实感觉还不错吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_03","textHome":"对我来说，那是理所当然的应对方法啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_37","textHome":"夜鹤随身携带的记事本是我做的好事笔记。上@面写着什么样的行动跟温柔有关，是我为了@她而记下来的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_38","textHome":"从我遇见月出里开始，她就一直没有很好的说@过话。不过不可思议的是夜鹤好像能理解她@想表达什么。也是挺有趣的呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_39","textHome":"哈……到了现在也完全搞不明白啊。要在恶意@中生存，该怎样才能战胜恶意…。只能够说@，这个世界真是让人恶心啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_40","textHome":"许下愿望而后又后悔，不知多少次能在绝望的@深渊里站稳脚步，我想是因为我找到了巨大@的存在。正因如此才能这样和平地生活下去"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_41","textHome":"嗯，啊——！今天心情真好啊。像这样的日子@就该去兜风转换心情。来这，坐在副驾驶座@上。我们到码头去看看吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_42","textHome":"那么，开始我们的表演时间吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_43","textHome":"认为只是调整的话，要尝尝苦头吗？"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_44","textHome":"在欢声中谢幕吧"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":104100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1041_00_45","textHome":"出了汗浑身黏糊糊的，回去的时候顺便去澡堂@吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,